{"tid":2192263,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"RubberBand出左新歌啦","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T14:46:20.000Z","uid":36283,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"59338c96983a4466511a5dd32e812a30fb113159","tid":2192263,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFBr93_f6BE&amp;ab_channel=RubberBand\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVFBr93_f6BE%26ab_channel%3DRubberBand&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=95cd7f64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFBr93_f6BE&amp;ab_channel=RubberBand</a><br />\n健兒<br />\n<br />\n起初，我們帶著對東京奧運2020的期望，構想一首力量歌兒。<br />\n奈何疫症叫停奧運，到現在仍有點不可思議。<br />\n<br />\n沒有奧運直播，人人做不成觀眾，卻差點沒發現自己一直是健兒。<br />\n奧運會是暫停了，可我們生命比賽一直沒有暫停，對手一波又一波：<br />\n名字叫做磨人困境，貧病交迫，有志難伸，窒息氣候，反覆疫情，當然還有最難纏老對手－－－那個不爭氣的自己。<br />\n<br />\n如果說I專輯裡《漫長》是揭開艱難時期布幔的序曲，《百毒不侵》能讓大家歇斯底理發洩，《健兒》就是伴隨大家同行於最壞時間的進行曲。<br />\n<br />\n在此特別鳴謝 A Capella 團隊AMuiXis - AMX 參與人聲和音。<br />\n<br />\n大家都要保持身心健康，迎難而上。"},{"pid":"08b61c0a6975db275ad9428c9aa4e3688903f2ce","tid":2192263,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"易健兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e282d5757f27d97dcb507c6c1cddec8466fc78","tid":2192263,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed57ebe8381ce67a4c2845006f9188fbbecffeff","tid":2192263,"uid":125905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"一首歌，幾重意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125fe5b1f7693ca4c73266ecc4c46537477bf472","tid":2192263,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"<i